{
  "doc_id": "34083",
  "text": "The third terms in Eqs. (2) and (3) are quite different, which is most pronounced when θ i is small. Experiments conducted by Xiao et al. [CITATION_1] in this regime confirm the accuracy of Eq. (3) and disprove Eq. (2). It is important to resolve this difference between the approaches because each has advantages in understanding the properties of a VIPA.",
